Women Empowerment, National e-Governance Award for Digital Land System, Saubhagya Yojana Award for more power connectivity and 3 national awards for Empowerment of Persons with Disabilities. The state also ranks first in milk, sugar, sugarcane and food production. The state is also a leader in establishment and operation of most medical institutions in the country.UP, with a huge population of 23 crore people, is moving towards becoming a one trillion dollar economy as envisioned by Prime Minister Narendra Modi.Our ideological vision, which embodies the concept of Rashtrodaya from Antyodaya is relentless in order to satisfy the desire of Awadh, the hope of Poorvanchal, the expectation of Bundelkhand and the aspirations of Paschimanchal. The action being taken by our system under zero tolerance on everyone involved in corruption and malpractices, has been successful in conveying the message of ‘changed system’.For inclusive development, we have presented a budget of Rs 5,12,860.72 crore, which is the biggest budget in the history of the state. In this historic budget dedicated to youth, schemes like Chief Minister’s Apprenticeship Promotion Scheme and Youth Entrepreneurship Development Campaign (YUVA) will prove to be milestones in the field of self-employment and self-reliance.It is the first step of the resolve to take the holy land of Lord Shri Ram and Shri Krishna to the highest glory with the inspiration of the prime minister. I am confident that the remaining 2 years will be in the direction of progress, public welfare and democracy.Yes, on the basis of the fulfilment of the promises made in 2017 elections, the foundation of a new UP has been laid.
